item.description:
Join us for a day of fall frolics at Wojcik's Farm in Blackstone, MA. We will be picking pumpkins, sampling caramel apples and hot apple cider, riding around on wagons, and possibly getting lost in a corn maze. Meet us at the Farm at noon. If you need a ride, or if you have a car and are willing to take others, please mention that in your RSVP so people can coordinate. Zak and I will rent a car and can be reached at 857-221-2140 or by email.

Information about the farm and driving directions are available at: http://www.wojcikfarm....
item.name: Fall Farm Festivities! (pumpkin picking, cider, corn maze, and hay rides)
